  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to soak up the sun and experience the ultimate camp adventure in a tropical paradise? Jump into the Gym Camp Simulator and transform your island into a fitness haven! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/87357c8d2203c2b5954f60bbc2f263ca.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=175 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/94d920cc5801deed2cc5782121eab31d.poster.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/94d920cc5801deed2cc5782121eab31d.webm?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/94d920cc5801deed2cc5782121eab31d.mp4?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build new facilities, design the interior, craft camp items, and optimize resources to keep the camp running smoothly. Manage your budget wisely to expand your camp with new buildings such as a dorm, gym, dining hall, spa, infirmary, and even kindergarten for parent campers to join the camp with their children!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/f216e5ba15d9626a7c6e6f286f1d220a.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/313b863dc7af1ec123a7cb9ba4700d9e.poster.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/313b863dc7af1ec123a7cb9ba4700d9e.webm?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/313b863dc7af1ec123a7cb9ba4700d9e.mp4?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Determine the right strategies to keep your guests satisfied. Make decisions to optimize the camp's operations, such as providing excellent daily programs and activities, managing your staff effectively, and increasing your camp level and ranking. Ensure campers well-being with staff such as nurses, chefs, trainers, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/0b805c68342bbf4201c8fdacd414550b.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=175 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/c022159e835018fa06c3b5846740369e.poster.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/c022159e835018fa06c3b5846740369e.webm?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/c022159e835018fa06c3b5846740369e.mp4?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monitor campers' progress and adjust schedules as needed to keep them on track and happy. Create custom workout routines and meal plans to help your guests achieve their fitness goals. Campers may suffer injuries during workouts, faint from hunger, or escape from the island! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/0c9ab174f08891741b4832268adf3f7b.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/dd24d2824ee59fce78c8b5c6bafb7308.poster.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/dd24d2824ee59fce78c8b5c6bafb7308.webm?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/dd24d2824ee59fce78c8b5c6bafb7308.mp4?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Organize various activities to boost the mood of your campers such as yoga sessions, challenging high-energy group classes, dance parties, and gatherings around the campfire to enjoy the camp vibes. Watch out for pirates and strangers, and ensure the safety of the camp!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/cded50009e230e8d156bc23955dbd7b1.poster.avif?t=1748103545\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/cded50009e230e8d156bc23955dbd7b1.webm?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/cded50009e230e8d156bc23955dbd7b1.mp4?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to soak up the sun and experience the ultimate camp adventure in a tropical paradise? Jump into the Gym Camp Simulator and transform your island into a fitness haven! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/87357c8d2203c2b5954f60bbc2f263ca.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=175 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/94d920cc5801deed2cc5782121eab31d.poster.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/94d920cc5801deed2cc5782121eab31d.webm?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/94d920cc5801deed2cc5782121eab31d.mp4?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build new facilities, design the interior, craft camp items, and optimize resources to keep the camp running smoothly. Manage your budget wisely to expand your camp with new buildings such as a dorm, gym, dining hall, spa, infirmary, and even kindergarten for parent campers to join the camp with their children!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/f216e5ba15d9626a7c6e6f286f1d220a.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/313b863dc7af1ec12