 escape from the island! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/0c9ab174f08891741b4832268adf3f7b.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/dd24d2824ee59fce78c8b5c6bafb7308.poster.avif?t=1748103545\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/dd24d2824ee59fce78c8b5c6bafb7308.webm?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/dd24d2824ee59fce78c8b5c6bafb7308.mp4?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Organize various activities to boost the mood of your campers such as yoga sessions, challenging high-energy group classes, dance parties, and gatherings around the campfire to enjoy the camp vibes. Watch out for pirates and strangers, and ensure the safety of the camp!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/cded50009e230e8d156bc23955dbd7b1.poster.avif?t=1748103545\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/cded50009e230e8d156bc23955dbd7b1.webm?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808950/extras/cded50009e230e8d156bc23955dbd7b1.mp4?t=1748103545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
